    p.btext I was just getting desperate enough to brave all the shame, and to seize it, when a window behind me was raised, and a gentleman spoke out of it, saying:
    p.btext "Step in here, please."
    p.btext I was admitted by a gorgeous flunkey, and shown into a sumptuous room where a couple of elderly gentlemen were sitting. They sent away the servant, and made me sit down.

    br

    p
      span.btext They had just finished their breakfast
      |
      |(они только что закончили свой завтрак;
      |
      span.f-coni to finish ['fInIS]
      |)
      span.btext , and the sight of the remains of it almost overpowered me
      |
